column1: ## Some summary parameters of the cross sections for atoms and molecules in the Leiden database
## cross_sect_ref:    Where to find a discussion of this cross section
## cross_sec_unc:     Uncertainty of cross section for wavelengths relevant to a stellar radiation field.
## Lyalpha_unc:       Uncertainty of cross section for wavelengths relevant to Lyman alpha radiation.
## cosmic_ray_unc:    Uncertainty of cross section for wavelengths relevant to a cosmic ray induced radiation field.
## Lyalpha_pd_xs:     The value of the photodissociation cross seciton at Lyman alpha (cm2).
## Lyalpha_pi_xs:     The value of the photoionisation cross seciton at Lyman alpha (cm2).
## pd_threshold:      The longest wavelength important photodissociation threshold (nm).
## pd_products :      The dominant fragments of photodissociation at its long wavelength threshold.
##  B: accurate within a factor of 2
##  C: accurate within a factor of 10
